# thoth_browser_enrollment

Creates and updates browser enrollment state for users/devices.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_browser_enrollment" "eng_laptop" {
  provider_name = "chrome"
  user_id       = "alice"
  device_id     = "macbook-001"
  status        = "active"
}
```
